Pulsar is an original implementation architecturally inspired by Netflix
Conductor (https://github.com/Netflix/conductor), which is licensed under the
Apache License 2.0. No source code from Netflix Conductor is included in or
derived for this project; Pulsar shares only high-level architectural
concepts common to workflow orchestration engines (DAG-based workflow
definitions, task queues, worker polling). Netflix Conductor and Netflix are
trademarks of Netflix, Inc., which is not affiliated with and does not
endorse this project.
